{"tid":2011621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解唔整一個毛五.藍絲既黑名單呢?","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T06:43:34.000Z","uid":193217,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16ed460c83af340728f8373d79170bcff21d3a00","tid":2011621,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"既然大家都知道有咁多五毛.藍絲.什至有政府<br />\n警狗入黎囉料<br />\n<br />\n點解唔集連登既所有力量.一齊長期block<br />\n柒班分化撚.疑似鬼既會員黎<br />\n而個post就長期熱門.等連登會員去參考<br />\n<br />\n我明白連登係一個言論自由既地方<br />\n但既然明知有咁撚多鬼就應該要開始<br />\n設立名單.為黎近佢想設立23條鋪路<br />\n<br />\n而為免有咁多鬼.或者五毛亂放人名<br />\n可以選擇cap圖既形式黎判斷<br />\n咁可以全香港人一齊監察<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我意見如何?"},{"pid":"93aed55a363959918d22c0c76b603a95cff84c79","tid":2011621,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"連登admin可以考慮下"},{"pid":"d74a987b388b89b6064d85cb548cbe1ebdfc699e","tid":2011621,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b04fdb550afb5149185159ced5eb0c877495b7d8","tid":2011621,"uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d74a987b388b89b6064d85cb548cbe1ebdfc699e","tid":2011621,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"唔係認真.而係真係有班人長期帶方向<br />\n而呢班人係有預謀"},{"pid":"51d9aa3bfc451bb6a80c9fdd18b0a1909a31965b","tid":2011621,"uid":264783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"4af3f07f858911a62ee6fad9051f6c18a5ef30ce","tid":2011621,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a800dbf26549435582d3fb44e0c016c3e114fe4","tid":2011621,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"而呢個名單.入左既會員可以有監察期<br />\n如果最終證明唔到佢地係內部既人.<br />\n就可以del"},{"pid":"